间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">（2）策略构建：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">尽管贪心选择可保证最优性，却可能丧失多样性。为此，ROVER 引入基于</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503515354\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.150943396226415\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"53\" style=\"width: 20px;height: 23px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfia7U9PicpZSR6nUrCyU72KXzFA6RvF5pnSs2iatJLuu4IZn9czKG0X0zjQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"1\" data-cropx2=\"54\" data-cropy1=\"3\" data-cropy2=\"64\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=950205d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaO3jPic1C3YywveH9gCJtYBXJKJ0oQKVFuyzvKbTexFibeHARDZxvLg3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">值的 softmax 采样：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515368\" data-ratio=\"0.22895622895622897\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"594\" style=\"width: 225px;height: 52px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31aa3c07&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfia6fkYQIjRW9UBnZFkttMkBOWpIHGUdv28VicjicZnVlxgKfrHSJnEicoww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其中</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503515427\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5294117647058822\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"34\" style=\"width:20px;height:31px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40ad27f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaGTaiazOrfOmTLjX13zriaIA043hsnDN4z6ZSDJNafS1LW2OwiaZ6clzNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是温度系数，控制探索程度。这种方式既保留了高价值路径的优先级，又能探索多条有效推理路线，显著提升 pass@k 表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">（3）训练目标：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在实际实现中，ROVER 还引入了：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503515354\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.150943396226415\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"53\" style=\"width: 20px;height: 23px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfia7U9PicpZSR6nUrCyU72KXzFA6RvF5pnSs2iatJLuu4IZn9czKG0X0zjQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"1\" data-cropx2=\"54\" data-cropy1=\"3\" data-cropy2=\"64\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=950205d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaO3jPic1C3YywveH9gCJtYBXJKJ0oQKVFuyzvKbTexFibeHARDZxvLg3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">函数内化于 LLM 参数，无需训练额外价值网络：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515373\" data-ratio=\"0.0880952380952381\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"840\" style=\"width: 278px;height: 24px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c144766c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaI1ovoCoMGI6iaKHznjs7EqZIpPiawyxPCXlXbbrebEBWPTloSZ1EAwGw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种「自监督」式参数化，让模型学习「相对改进」而非「绝对价值」，既减少计算量，又提升稳定性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">组内奖励中心化，降低方差，即&nbsp;</span><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515374\" data-ratio=\"0.19727891156462585\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"294\" style=\"width: 141px;height: 28px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=262b6d9c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaqUtZqHcM0VRk50Ria953icbjTibTN3bukLib4xegda1Tm9gOr6scSd0pfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。避免高方差奖励干扰</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503515354\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.150943396226415\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"53\" style=\"width: 20px;height: 23px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfia7U9PicpZSR6nUrCyU72KXzFA6RvF5pnSs2iatJLuu4IZn9czKG0X0zjQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"1\" data-cropx2=\"54\" data-cropy1=\"3\" data-cropy2=\"64\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=950205d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaO3jPic1C3YywveH9gCJtYBXJKJ0oQKVFuyzvKbTexFibeHARDZxvLg3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">值学习。同时，将中心化奖励「广播」到生成的全序列 token，实现细粒度信用分配。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ROVER 的损失函数可以表示为</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515375\" data-ratio=\"0.1383177570093458\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1070\" style=\"width: 365px;height: 50px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a6e4651&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaZ7Nk0PtWh5b8iavz87Da4X1Nspb8qHINNpe30pwBAVvia0tnnwPiajecA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">算法伪代码如下</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515376\" data-ratio=\"0.41574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 463px;height: 192px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3793681&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaybkNpdJoAy5wCynAD5hTkExXYHDicWicMRzns3n8PlCwRGYGygSGIMZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验结果：全面领先，多样性显著提升</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队在数学推理基准（AIME24/25、HMMT25、AMC、MATH 等）、Countdown 任务以及 O.O.D. 任务 GPQA-diamond 上验证 ROVER，覆盖 Qwen3-8B/4B、DeepSeek-R1-1.5B 等模型，结果堪称「降维打击」：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">1. 数学竞赛任务：pass@1 与 pass@k 双突破</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Qwen3-8B-Base 模型上，ROVER 的 pass@1 在 AIME24 达 30.6（比最佳基线 DAPO 高 19.1 分）；在 HMMT25 任务中，pass@1 从基线最高 7.1 跃升至 14.6（提升 106%）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515377\" data-ratio=\"0.4935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3243a360&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaGUWygRqviaDP7g7dOhH7VoPHYQKOdouLbhyJ6nbPF8YoTvOP6YOmXyQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更关键的是 pass@k 性能：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">传统 RL 方法（如 GRPO）的 pass@k 随 k 增大迅速饱和，而</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">ROVER 在 pass@256 上也能与基线拉开明显差距，展现持续探索能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515378\" data-ratio=\"0.37777777777777777\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0e02aeee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiaJkFmLibbhp00pBgibukqm4T2ZDS9Xq5tYmicEqjRicYYYoJp6krabWBcPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 策略多样性：比基线高 17.6%，覆盖更多解题路径</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">采用 LLM-as-Judge 方法评判所有方法生成的正确答案的推理内容多样性，ROVER 训练的策略多样性比基线平均提升 +17.6%，在 AIME24 上发现更多独特解题路径。在其他多样性指标如余弦距离（cosine distance）与利用率（utility）等，ROVER 在不同温度下仍表现出一致的高多样性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">受益于多样性的提升，ROVER 在 GPQA-diamond 等与数学无关的 O.O.D 任务上也表现最佳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515379\" data-ratio=\"0.3101851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 534px;height: 166px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b0632427&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfia9No4ic640nDDYP44bV5HVctY54pI0FbHVJBcibdrlT9X3YZ5WZBOnWUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">3. 案例展示：ROVER 发现全新解法</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过「策略数量」指标（同一问题生成的不同推理路径数）评估，&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">ROVER 在各个任务上均能发现更多的解题策略。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如下图所示，在「2x3 网格数字排列」问题中，基模型与 GRPO 均仅发现 2 种策略，而 ROVER 可以发现 4 种（包括「隔板法」「容斥原理」等不同数学工具）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503515380\" data-ratio=\"0.875\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b23b758d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9aLxwS9wAZl5cBUyvFmYfiacXO0iaYXnjkiaxicmCSAqibd96iaafa8SnlJzI0XNEVLEeCDUQYmeKQx3kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">启示与展望</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ROVER 的提出，不仅是一次技术突破，更是一次方法论的反思：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">在某些结构化任务中，简化而非复杂化，才是推进性能的关键。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication.」 —— ROVER 这一基于简单随机策略的新方法，诠释了达芬奇这句名言在 AI 时代的新内涵。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更多方法细节与实验分析请见原论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "港科大团队提出 ROVER 算法，通过对随机策略进行价值评估，简化大模型数学推理范式，显著提升性能和多样性，并已开源。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "港科大团队提出 ROVER 算法，通过对随机策略进行价值评估，简化大模型数学推理范式，显著提升性能和多样性，并已开源。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了香港科技大学团队提出的 ROVER（Random Policy Valuation for Diverse Reasoning）算法，旨在革新大语言模型（LLM）的数学推理范式。传统强化学习方法在 LLM 推理任务中常面临训练不稳定、多样性丧失和调参复杂等问题。ROVER 基于一个颠覆性发现：在特定马尔可夫决策过程（MDP）结构下，均匀随机策略的 Q 值足以指导最优策略。该算法通过三步极简流程——Q 值估计、策略构建和训练目标，避免了传统策略迭代的复杂性，无需额外维护价值网络或基模型。实验结果显示，ROVER 在多项数学推理基准（如 AIME24/25、HMMT25）上显著超越现有方法，大幅提升了 pass@1 和 pass@k 性能，并使推理策略多样性提高 17.6%，甚至能发现全新解法。该研究强调了在特定结构化任务中，“简化而非复杂化”是提升性能的关键，并已开源论文、代码和模型。",
